{"tid":2497902,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Airtag—遺失東西的習慣，消失了。","createTime":"2021-04-20T22:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T23:44:41.000Z","uid":114873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5529ed1b19406179edd937978c0f65edc4064a0","tid":2497902,"uid":114873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T22:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUaUeNVEBAF1vUS5wu59iJGPE11ZUKQBRgDosf1gfCBSk?filename=fayvDJT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfayvDJT.png&h=2dac8b28&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTwj7JFmigj1o9EubcW3frppC8zgBqa3et8WPTMakxxPB?filename=42bX3aA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42bX3aA.png&h=d6838f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAirTag 讓你超級輕鬆地追蹤你的物品。扣一個在鎖匙，再放一個入背囊。就這樣，你就能透過尋找 app 找到它們的位置。你還可以在 app 內追蹤 Apple 裝置，並緊貼親朋好友的動向。<br />\n<br />\n呼叫它，找到它。<br />\n只要加個 AirTag 在銀包之類的物品，就算你記不起它放在哪裡，都不用擔心。前往尋找 app 的全新「物品」分頁，或直接講「喂 Siri，搵吓我個銀包」，就能透過內置揚聲器播放音效。如果它就在附近，像在梳化底或隔壁房間，只需跟著聲音便能找到它的藏身之處。<br />\n<br />\n近，好近，<br />\n非常近，搵到。<br />\n如果你的 AirTag 就在附近，iPhone 就能透過精確尋找功能，帶你直接找到它1。多得超寬頻技術，你可以看到你與 AirTag 的距離和往哪個方向可以找到它。<br />\n<br />\n多得千千萬萬人的一臂之力。<br />\n如果你在沙灘或健身室等較遠的地方遺留了物品，尋找 app 網絡，能助你追蹤 AirTag 的所在。這個龐大的網絡由全球數以億計的 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 裝置組成。精心的設計，更讓你的私隱時刻得到保護。<br />\n<br />\n何來神通廣大?<br />\n你的 AirTag 會發出安全的藍牙訊號，被尋找 app 網絡中的附近裝置偵測到。這些裝置會將你的 AirTag 位置傳送到 iCloud，讓你可在尋找 app 的地圖上看到它。一切過程完全匿名，而且經過加密保護，以保障你的私隱。尋找過程別具效率，你不必擔心電池使用時間或數據用量。<br />\n<br />\nHK$239 起"},{"pid":"010c54e5be35e81081aab1e59db59a239d9a1e85","tid":2497902,"uid":252920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T22:47:47.000Z","msg":"放落條女度"},{"pid":"e8e13ecc6ff9799d75c3b9a347b31def5ce318d9","tid":2497902,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T22:59:02.000Z","msg":"又無講可以搵到幾遠嘅嘢<br />\n例如我住屯門，但件野漏低係馬鞍山，咁又搵唔搵到？"},{"pid":"5805ea9f0bdc326412d0dfdc519de4325e0ca32a","tid":2497902,"uid":92633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:02:02.000Z","msg":"一粒BLE tag 賣咁貴？"},{"pid":"e71d46d8cdcee714c5a82f9280db161521ce5ced","tid":2497902,"uid":129895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e13ecc6ff9799d75c3b9a347b31def5ce318d9","tid":2497902,"uid":47775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T22:59:02.000Z","msg":"又無講可以搵到幾遠嘅嘢<br />\n例如我住屯門，但件野漏低係馬鞍山，咁又搵唔搵到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:04:55.000Z","msg":"跌咗喺地球另一邊都搵到"},{"pid":"78107b0290012b1e0e29ddcdbe4b959026cf52b4","tid":2497902,"uid":17359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:06:32.000Z","msg":"共產黨：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da63b22d09b5bf95c44a3e8574f9e8bfb9445bff","tid":2497902,"uid":22590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:08:00.000Z","msg":"世界末日了<br />\n個Apps可以加家人朋友<br />\n即係你去到邊都會被人追蹤"},{"pid":"964084c7cc6d06c57f7d4475ba3bdef4e4115154","tid":2497902,"uid":227066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:20:58.000Z","msg":"想知洗唔洗成日叉電  想買舊擺落26度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d4b733864fe4c2023d51869d78dbbd37a234ab","tid":2497902,"uid":129895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"964084c7cc6d06c57f7d4475ba3bdef4e4115154","tid":2497902,"uid":227066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:20:58.000Z","msg":"想知洗唔洗成日叉電  想買舊擺落26度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkg